1
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:23,524
 ♫ Chasing wind, I set out afar ♫ 

2
00:00:23,524 --> 00:00:27,115
 ♫ The road ahead lost, my voice unheard ♫ 

3
00:00:27,115 --> 00:00:29,176
 ♫ I've tasted joy and sorrow ♫ 

4
00:00:29,176 --> 00:00:32,561
 ♫ Laying low, I plan every move ♫ 

5
00:00:32,561 --> 00:00:36,140
 ♫ With a mortal heart and lingering ties ♫ 

6
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,960
 ♫ I'm roaming far and wide ♫ 

7
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:41,960
 ♫ A twist of fate in desperate times ♫ 

8
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:46,511
 ♫ A bond that outlives the dust of life ♫ 

9
00:00:46,511 --> 00:00:50,985
 ♫ Still chasing what immortality means ♫ 

10
00:00:50,985 --> 00:00:56,252
 ♫ Even eternity flashes by in a blink ♫ 

11
00:00:59,034 --> 00:01:01,280
 ♫ Don't mock my ordinary life ♫ 

12
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:05,760
 ♫ I fight alone as chaos shakes the world ♫ 

13
00:01:08,057 --> 00:01:10,272
 ♫ Don't scorn my humble roots ♫ 

14
00:01:10,272 --> 00:01:13,620
 ♫ Kind at heart, ruthless when I must be ♫ 

15
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:15,678
 ♫ Fate stirs with joy and grief beneath ♫ 

16
00:01:15,678 --> 00:01:17,982
 ♫ I hold the tide between life and death ♫ 

17
00:01:17,982 --> 00:01:20,175
 ♫ Faith carries me through endless dark ♫ 

18
00:01:20,175 --> 00:01:22,855
 ♫ And I return with a heart refined ♫ 

19
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:30,001
 ♫ Forged by trial, I rise through three realms ♫ 

20
00:01:30,001 --> 00:01:33,580
 ♫ Reborn in the wheel of fate ♫ 

21
00:01:33,580 --> 00:01:34,780
 

22
00:01:34,780 --> 00:01:36,020
 

23
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:39,780
 

24
00:01:50,670 --> 00:01:51,800
Caught you.

25
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:54,082
Are you fleeing the battle?

26
00:01:54,082 --> 00:01:56,662
Meng, cut it out.

27
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,694
Han,

28
00:01:59,694 --> 00:02:01,785
I got these pills on my last mission

29
00:02:01,785 --> 00:02:03,870
to help with recovery and strengthening.

30
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:04,920
Take them.

31
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,540
Just in case.

32
00:02:07,670 --> 00:02:09,100
You've all heard.

33
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:12,530
The Master trusts us the most.

34
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,880
Here. Take it.

35
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,560
Thanks.

36
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:20,560
Han, why not ask Master to let me go with you?

37
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,880
It's not easy to find a good sparring partner.

38
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:25,000
I haven't had enough fun yet.

39
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,710
The war is in full swing.

40
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:28,640
You trying to dodge the fight?

41
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,530
Who said I was dodging?

42
00:02:31,488 --> 00:02:34,110
Han, come here a second.

43
00:02:34,110 --> 00:02:38,390
I heard there's a new
cosmetics shop in the capital.

44
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:39,985
The Moxiang Abode.

45
00:02:39,985 --> 00:02:42,430
They sell all kinds of skincare and perfumes.

46
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:44,888
Pick some up for me, will you?

47
00:02:44,888 --> 00:02:46,400
I made a list.

48
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,280
Just follow it.

49
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,570
Don't let Senior Liu find out.

50
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,350
 Things look lively. 

51
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:59,310
 That brat. 

52
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:01,980
 Let's see how he acts when he sees me on my ark. 

53
00:03:23,350 --> 00:03:25,760
 If she doesn't want to see me, 

54
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:30,420
 then I'll just pretend we're strangers,
like she said. 

55
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:40,280
 What's that supposed to mean? 

56
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,090
 He didn't even say hi. 

57
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,710
Where are you going?

58
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:46,000
Aft cabin.

59
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,310
 You brat. 

60
00:03:47,310 --> 00:03:49,210
 You didn't even look at me. 

61
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:26,500
 Who do you think you are, huh? 

62
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:58,840
 Nangong Wan. 

63
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,680
 You're already in the Core Formation Stage. 

64
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:03,120
 Why are you still mad over some nobody? 

65
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,910
 It's not worth it. 

66
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:06,370
 I'm not mad. 

67
00:05:08,978 --> 00:05:10,680
Calm down.

68
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:13,881
Who he's with, who he's buying rouge for,

69
00:05:13,881 --> 00:05:16,430
has nothing to do with me!

70
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:18,140
He's not even worthy.

71
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,270
This is maddening!

72
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:55,720
I'm going to forget him.

73
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,610
I have to forget him!

74
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:00,730
Back to my cultivating.

75
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:10,190
Han Li...

76
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:12,290
I'll never forgive you.

77
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,260
She wouldn't

78
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,820
really kill me, would she?

79
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,560
 That should be Yuanwu Kingdom. 

80
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,040
 A good chance to find Qi Yun Xiao 

81
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,750
 and the array master he serves 

82
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,650
 to ask about the teleport array. 

83
00:06:40,310 --> 00:06:44,140
Mr. Han, we're not in the capital yet.

84
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,310
I have a mission.

85
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,850
I'll take my leave.

86
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:56,430
Right. One more thing.

87
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:58,650
Please pass this to Senior Nangong.

88
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,700
What is it?

89
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,580
Ageless Pill.

90
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,090
Ageless Pill?

91
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,830
Grandmaster,

92
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,830
that guy in the back cabin left.

93
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,070
He left?

94
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:30,050
Looked like he headed toward Yuanwu Kingdom.

95
00:07:31,065 --> 00:07:33,115
He didn't even come to see me.

96
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,830
He told me to give you this.

97
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,510
Give me what?

98
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,600
It's a pill.

99
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,600
He said it's the Ageless Pill.

100
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,170
Ageless Pill?

101
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:46,340
What for? Does he think I'm old?

102
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:54,070
- You may go.
- Yes.

103
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:56,800
Wait. Don't tell anyone about this.

104
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,380
Especially not my senior Ni Chang.

105
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,940
Forget it. I'll let you off this time.

106
00:08:57,940 --> 00:09:01,920
 

107
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,600
Shouldn't you be minding the shop?

108
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,970
Where did you go?

109
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:09,720
 

110
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,800
Top-grade artifact, the Flamecloud Sword.

111
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,190
It has fire-element techniques.

112
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:16,360
Personally refined by a Core Formation cultivator.

113
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,920
Starting bid. 200 gems.

114
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,340
Any takers?

115
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,920
- I'll bid 300.
- 300.

116
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:24,950
- I bid 400.
- 400.

117
00:09:24,950 --> 00:09:27,120
400 gems! Any more bids?

118
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,950
- 500.
- 500 gems!

119
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:30,680
Anyone going higher?

120
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:33,160
-  This auction's on another level... 
- 500, once.

121
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,920
-  These are all Early Foundation Establishment. 
- 500, twice.

122
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,360
500, thrice.

123
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,530
Sold!

124
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,460
Congratulations to the bidder.

125
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,950
Alright. Next item.

126
00:09:44,950 --> 00:09:46,870
Let's bring it up.

127
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:49,830
High-grade pill, Ageless Pill.

128
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:50,932
- Two pills.
- Ageless Pill?

129
00:09:50,932 --> 00:09:52,720
Ageless Pill! I want one too!

130
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:55,810
- This pill comes from the Joyful Union Sect.
- I want it!

131
00:09:55,810 --> 00:09:58,190
- I want it too!
- It's rare in the market.

132
00:09:58,190 --> 00:10:00,120
If you know, you know.

133
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:02,480
Starting bid. 100 gems.

134
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,390
This stuff is good. I want this one.

135
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:06,240
- I bid one-thirty.
- You're a grown man.

136
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,150
Why do you need the Ageless Pill?

137
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:09,910
Do you have no shame?

138
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,790
- 150.
- 150!

139
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:13,790
- 250.
- 250!

140
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:15,390
- 300.
- 300 gems!

141
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:16,910
- 500.
- 500 gems!

142
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,670
Any higher offers?

143
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:21,000
Looks do matter in cultivation.

144
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,000
These two Ageless Pills might sell

145
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:25,320
for as much as a top-tier artifact.

146
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,150
500, thrice.

147
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,320
Sold!

148
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,440
Congratulations, cultivator!

149
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,120
Excellent.

150
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,910
Please collect your item at the counter.

151
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:38,750
Esteemed guests, next up,
the 28th item of the night.

152
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:41,630
It's also the final item this month.

153
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:43,220
Golden Glow Ganoderma.

154
00:10:44,315 --> 00:10:46,450
- Now that's rare.
- A millennium-old one.

155
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,120
1,000 years old!

156
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:51,050
No starting bid set.

157
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:54,480
- Smells amazing...
-  Isn't that the one I sold... 

158
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,510
 To Treasure House? 

159
00:10:56,510 --> 00:11:00,480
 Is that shady merchant
actually backing this auction? 

160
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,120
- 1,800!
- 2,000!

161
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,360
- 2,000!
- 2,500!

162
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,910
2,500! Anyone higher?

163
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,510
- 2,500!
- 2,800!

164
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:07,610
2,800!

165
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:09,630
- 3,300!
- 3,300!

166
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:12,105
- 3,800!
- 3,800!

167
00:11:12,105 --> 00:11:14,630
- 3,800, once!
- Hold it!

168
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,020
Qi Yun Xiao?

169
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:20,600
This Millennium Ganoderma shall be mine.

170
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,910
Stop causing trouble!

171
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,550
Guards, throw him out!

172
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,100
-  Not this again! 
- Who even are you?

173
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:27,490
- I'll trade an array for it!
-  Still haven't learned, huh? 

174
00:11:27,490 --> 00:11:28,480
- This time... 
- Wait!

175
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,360
 he even dropped the disguise. 

176
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,870
Esteemed elders,

177
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:35,165
I am Qi Yun Xiao,
an Artifact Crafter in this city.

178
00:11:35,165 --> 00:11:38,880
I truly need that Golden
Glow Ganoderma to save a life.

179
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:42,882
I'm willing to offer two high-grade
arrays in exchange for it.

180
00:11:42,882 --> 00:11:44,320
Where did this guy come from?

181
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,480
Two arrays, you say?

182
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,812
- I have eight myself!
- Throw him out!

183
00:11:47,812 --> 00:11:49,400
- I'm just trying to...
- Kid, stand down!

184
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:52,320
- Get lost.
- Hold on, wait!

185
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:54,690
Young man, come back next time.

186
00:11:56,510 --> 00:11:57,670
- Come on.
- Elder, please!

187
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:59,150
I really need it to save a life.

188
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:01,750
- Elder, wait!
-  A Qi Refining rookie? 

189
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:03,510
-  An Artifact Crafter? 
- Move it.

190
00:12:03,510 --> 00:12:04,750
- 4,000!
- Elder!

191
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:05,950
- 4,000!
- To save a life!

192
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:08,790
4,000! Anyone want to bid higher?

193
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:10,720
- 4,500!
- 4,500!

194
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,840
- 4,800!
- 4,800!

195
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,380
Any bid higher than 4,800?

196
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,240
Blade Arts?

197
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,550
You're from the Fu Clan?

198
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:07,670
Now that you know, even
if you hand over the array,

199
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:09,500
we still can't let you live.

200
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,570
Han!

201
00:13:28,780 --> 00:13:35,220
 

202
00:13:38,771 --> 00:13:39,790
 

203
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:41,000
Yun Xiao.

204
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,480
Ru Yin?

205
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,790
How did you get hurt?

206
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,550
I let my guard down for a moment,

207
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:47,790
and some thugs mugged me.

208
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:49,550
-  Is this girl... 
- Han saved me.

209
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:51,740
 the one he cares so much about? 

210
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:56,650
Han, come in.

211
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,670
The Millennium Spirit Herb you took earlier

212
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:05,690
was the one he traded to us.

213
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:11,030
Yun Xiao often mentioned you.

214
00:14:11,030 --> 00:14:12,910
You saved me once.

215
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:15,500
I, Xin Ru Yin, am deeply grateful.

216
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:21,780
Senior Han, come inside.

217
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:32,680
Han, you might not know,

218
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:37,910
those two are from the Fu Clan,
the top family in Yuanwu.

219
00:14:37,910 --> 00:14:39,240
They are trouble.

220
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,870
My advice? Leave here soon.

221
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:43,630
You stepped in to protect me.

222
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,690
I don't want to get you involved.

223
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:51,480
Just now, I wiped out all their traces.

224
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,980
I won't stay long.

225
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:59,360
However, I think you two
should find somewhere quiet

226
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:02,290
and lay low just to be safe.

227
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:07,080
Ru Yin, did you hear that?

228
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:10,910
Han says we should find a quiet place
and stay a while.

229
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,870
Yun Xiao,

230
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:15,100
we're not even married yet.

231
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:23,150
By the way, Han, thanks to Ru Yin's help,

232
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,550
the upgrade for the Five Phases
Reversing Array went smoothly.

233
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:27,720
Its defense is stronger now,

234
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:30,440
plus it now has an illusory trap
to restrain enemies.

235
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,870
I'll go get it.

236
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:34,380
Qi, no rush.

237
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:37,840
Since Miss Ru Yin is here too,

238
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:42,140
I actually came to ask for your help
to appraise something.

239
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:48,630
Teleportation, stabilization, acceleration,

240
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:51,330
spiritual channeling, amplification.

241
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:56,240
I can't believe this ancient teleport array
actually exists.

242
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:59,030
Once this array is infused with spiritual power,

243
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:01,810
it can teleport across great distances.

244
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:06,480
It seems you also need
a Greater Teleport Command Seal

245
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:08,810
to withstand spatial turbulence.

246
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,870
Judging by your expression,

247
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:15,860
that shouldn't be a problem for you.

248
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:20,510
Unfortunately, this array isn't complete.

249
00:16:20,510 --> 00:16:22,360
A part is missing.

250
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,220
It may no longer be usable.

251
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:28,720
Do you think you can restore it?

252
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:32,320
This array is very ancient,
and part of it is broken.

253
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:35,750
To fix it would take rare high-grade materials.

254
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:37,810
It also involves a secret art.

255
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:42,510
Right now, I'm still unwell.

256
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:46,000
I'm afraid we're not able to help you with it.

257
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,900
We're truly sorry.

258
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:53,000
If it's about the cost, don't worry.

259
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,780
I'll handle all of it.

260
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:58,120
I still have Golden Glow Ganoderma.

261
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:59,690
I can trade it.

262
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:11,240
Ru Yin, your illness can be cured.

263
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,320
Let's just agree to it.

264
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:14,630
Don't worry, Han. I'll figure it out.

265
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:20,360
Yun Xiao, my condition comes from
being born with the Dragon Roar Body.

266
00:17:20,360 --> 00:17:24,440
As I cultivate, my meridians gradually wither.

267
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:26,480
