534
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:54,110
Lately, I've told those five idiots

535
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:56,850
to search the capital for rogue cultivators.

536
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,710
Miss Mo?

537
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:16,320
Why are you here?

538
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:18,140
You're here too?

539
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:24,060
You're tailing Steward Wang?

540
00:36:25,510 --> 00:36:27,280
He's the one I told you about.

541
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,480
He wiped out my clan,

542
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:30,230
Sect Leader of the Five-Color Sect.

543
00:36:30,230 --> 00:36:31,630
He's dangerous.

544
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:33,620
Way out of your league.

545
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:39,070
Is he a cultivator?

546
00:36:39,070 --> 00:36:40,490
More or less.

547
00:36:41,230 --> 00:36:42,710
But he reeks of dark aura.

548
00:36:42,710 --> 00:36:43,960
Clearly a demonic type.

549
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:45,410
Not a righteous man.

550
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:49,200
I should've figured.

551
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:53,860
Everything he said
and all those shady dealings...

552
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:58,805
How are there so many cultivators in the world,

553
00:36:58,805 --> 00:37:01,065
and I just happen to meet them all?

554
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:08,480
Miss Mo, this place is dangerous.

555
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,000
Before anyone sees you, go back.

556
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:11,700
Don't come again.

557
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:21,890
Li.

558
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,260
I thought

559
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:29,290
I'd never see you again.

560
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:33,920
On the day we parted at the Yan Clan Stronghold,

561
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:36,260
you didn't say anything.

562
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:38,930
But I knew

563
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:42,660
a mortal like me who can't cultivate

564
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:47,370
could never walk the same path as you.

565
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:50,890
Our lives are far too short,

566
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:55,490
like morning dew that will be gone in a blink.

567
00:37:56,320 --> 00:38:00,060
All love, hate, longing will turn to dust.

568
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:04,030
But even with such a fleeting life,

569
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:06,370
I still want to make it count.

570
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:09,320
Even if it's like a moth to a flame,

571
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:13,960
even if it ends in nothing, I still want to try.

572
00:38:13,960 --> 00:38:16,370
- But you...
- Li!

573
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:21,590
All these years,

574
00:38:21,590 --> 00:38:23,330
you haven't changed

575
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:26,810
a single bit.

576
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,700
Don't worry.

577
00:38:44,670 --> 00:38:48,710
Today, I won't kill him.

578
00:38:48,710 --> 00:38:51,540
I won't go head-on with him again.

579
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:56,510
I'll do as you and Father taught me.

580
00:38:56,510 --> 00:38:59,960
I'll do it one step at a time,

581
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:02,000
find his weakness and trap him,

582
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,450
until the day I can kill him.

583
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:08,800
No matter how it's done,

584
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:11,220
no matter how long it takes.

585
00:40:08,110 --> 00:40:09,850
Farewell,

586
00:40:11,510 --> 00:40:13,220
Li.

587
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,450
Miss Mo.

588
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:57,620
If I told you to stop, you wouldn't listen.

589
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:06,810
Very well, then.

590
00:41:34,670 --> 00:41:36,930
 You've been compromised. 

591
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:40,140
 Do you admit your guilt? 

592
00:41:46,190 --> 00:41:49,070
I was too blind to see your powerful presence.

593
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:52,780
Please, spare me!

594
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:00,180
Senior,

595
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:04,190
I am just a newcomer here.

596
00:42:04,190 --> 00:42:07,030
All I've done is enjoy some mortal offerings.

597
00:42:07,030 --> 00:42:09,630
I don't know

598
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:12,070
what crime I've committed.

599
00:42:12,070 --> 00:42:16,590
 Whether you have or not, that's for me to decide. 

600
00:42:16,590 --> 00:42:20,190
I'll ask the questions. Answer truthfully.

601
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:21,800
Yes! Yes!

602
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:24,070
-  You may rise. 
- Thank you, Senior.

603
00:42:24,070 --> 00:42:25,850
Many thanks, Senior.

604
00:42:28,710 --> 00:42:30,030
 What is your name? 

605
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:32,110
 Who is your master? 

606
00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:35,510
 That Fire Control Technique
you used back in the hall, 

607
00:42:35,510 --> 00:42:38,400
 where did you learn it? 

608
00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:40,510
Senior,

609
00:42:40,510 --> 00:42:41,550
I'm Wu San Xing.

610
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:43,000
I have no sect or master.

611
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:45,150
I'm just a rogue cultivator.

612
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:48,452
As for that spell, I developed it

613
00:42:48,452 --> 00:42:52,000
through my own practice and knowledge.

614
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:55,880
It was a simple trick to fool the mortals.

615
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:57,850
I meant no offense.

616
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:04,230
If you like it, I'm willing

617
00:43:04,230 --> 00:43:06,760
to offer it up with both hands.

618
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:08,920
 A smooth talker. 

619
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:11,080
 Clearly used to dealing in the mortal world 

620
00:43:11,080 --> 00:43:12,931
 and very street smart. 

621
00:43:12,931 --> 00:43:14,981
 Quite impressive. 

