00:44:19,080 --> 00:44:22,200
 ♫ Eyes once looked far ♫ 

633
00:44:22,200 --> 00:44:26,641
 ♫ Now lost in the shift ♫ 

634
00:44:26,641 --> 00:44:29,762
 ♫ Autumn winds stir ♫ 

635
00:44:29,762 --> 00:44:32,343
 ♫ Smoke curls once more ♫ 

636
00:44:32,343 --> 00:44:35,259
 ♫ Like clouds on the edge of sky ♫ 

637
00:44:35,259 --> 00:44:39,340
 ♫ Returning to my eyes ♫ 

638
00:44:39,340 --> 00:44:42,795
 ♫ Looking back from the mountaintop ♫ 

639
00:44:42,795 --> 00:44:45,720
 ♫ Time lost its name ♫ 

640
00:44:45,720 --> 00:44:49,046
 ♫ Was it yesterday ♫ 

641
00:44:49,046 --> 00:44:53,240
 ♫ Or tomorrow? ♫ 

